10:
M-Mew-Mew's okay. Just a little 
headache...
Why're humans so LOUD? Is it 'cause 
meowr ears are so small?
13: It WAS pretty loud and crowded, huh?
15:
Why don't you sit and rest for a minute 
while I pick up a quest?
21:
Myaaah... This is the biggest city Mew-
Mew's ever seen. Who mew the market 
would be THAT busy?
23:
A-and there were some MEAN looking 
adventurers! Mew-Mew's heard scary 
rumowrs about the strays lurking in 
the alleys...
25:
H-hopefully Alk won't mind walking 
Mew-Mew home later...
28:
Hey. Never seen YOU 'round these 
parts.
33:
M-mew're mew?! Mew-Mew doesn't 
talk to strangers!
36:
Those ears and tail—are you 
a gargan? I've heard about them, but 
it's my first time seeing one in person!
40:
Gargan?! Those giants?! Mew-Mew's 
beastfolk! Just, mew know... Mew-
Mew's a sphynx cat, so... no fur…
43:
Oh, really? Well you're adorable either 
way!
48:
You're sooo cute!
Mind if I sit with you? I'd love to hear 
more about you! Where are you from?
50:
You must be a new adventurer, right? 
Haha, I'd love to take you out and 
show you around town—we can stop 
by the Kaleidoscope too!
52:
Oh! And those are your real ears, right? 
What's it like having cat ears? Can 
I touch them? Lemme feel your tail 
too!
54: Try saying that one more time.
60:
Mew-Mew said try saying that one 
more time! Right meow!
62:
Gulp— Um, le- let me feel your tail? 
...Please?
65: Not that! What mew said before that!
67: ...I'd love to show you around town?
89:
Oh, uh, would you look at the time! 
I've gotta—
96: Ugh, I can't do this. Never mind...
102:
Can mew believe it? He was sooo 
flustered, he ran away! Mew-Mew's just 
mew darn cute!
106:
So much for wanting to be rough and 
rugged, huh?
108:
Well, guess the cutesy act suits you 
better than tryin' to put the "beast" in 
beastfolk.
113: Tsssss! How could mew say that?!
117:
Mew-Mew can be a cute kitty AND 
a cool cat! Just mew wait!
126:
Hmm, I dunno, I think she could pull it 
off. I still can't believe that guy beat 
me to the punch, though...
128:
I've been wanting to pet your ears for 
ages. They look so soft... I wish I had 
cat ears.
131:
Great, now even ALK wants to be cat-
like?
